## Exercise 1: Decorate the Corners

Place one beeper in each corner of the 5×5 world: (1,1), (5,1), (5,5), and (1,5).

Karel starts at (1, 1) facing east with an unlimited supply of beepers. Think about the pattern: you need to place a beeper and move to the next corner, four times. Can you write a function for that repeated step?

> **Hint:** After placing a beeper, Karel needs to move 4 spaces to reach the next corner, then turn left to be ready for the next side.

