## Exercise 2: Build a Plus Sign

Build a plus (+) sign centered at (3, 3) by placing beepers at these positions:

- **Vertical bar:** (3,1), (3,2), (3,3), (3,4), (3,5)
- **Horizontal bar:** (1,3), (2,3), (3,3), (4,3), (5,3)
- **Note:** This will result in **2 beepers** on (3,3).

Karel starts at (3, 1) facing north with an unlimited supply of beepers. Think about how to break this into pieces.

